    <h3>Move Beyond REST: Persistent Connections for Agents</h3>
    <p>REST polling wastes 98.5% of requests. WebSockets break at scale. Persistent bidirectional connections solve real-time agent communication without the infrastructure pain.</p>
    <div class="meta"><span class="date">Feb 26</span><span>Architecture</span><span class="tag">REST</span><span class="tag">real-time</span></div>
    </div>
  </a>

  <a class="blog-card" href="lightweight-swarm-communication-drones-robots.html">
