    <h3>Smart Home Without Cloud: Local-First Device Communication</h3>
    <p>Insteon died overnight, Wemo cloud ended in 2026, Google IoT Core shut down. Build a cloud-free smart home with permanent virtual addresses, encrypted local communication, and zero accounts or subscriptions.</p>
