    </div>
  </a>

  <a class="blog-card" href="build-ai-agent-marketplace-discovery-reputation.html">
    <img src="banners/build-ai-agent-marketplace-discovery-reputation.png" alt="" loading="lazy">
    <div class="card-body">
    <h3>Build an AI Agent Marketplace With Discovery and Reputation</h3>
    <p>Solve the ghost agent problem. Tag-based capability discovery, cryptographic trust handshakes, and polo score reputation create a self-regulating agent marketplace without a centralized platform.</p>
    <div class="meta"><span class="date">Feb 24</span><span>Architecture</span><span class="tag">marketplace</span><span class="tag">discovery</span></div>
    </div>
  </a>

