    <div class="card-body">
    <h3>Secure Research Collaboration: Share Models, Not Data</h3>
    <p>Cross-institutional ML collaboration without sharing raw data. Encrypted model weight exchange, trust-gated connections as collaboration agreements, and self-hosted infrastructure for HIPAA/GDPR environments.</p>
    <div class="meta"><span class="date">Feb 23</span><span>Research</span><span class="tag">privacy</span><span class="tag">federated-learning</span></div>
    </div>
  </a>

