---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead title="Blog" description="Technical articles about building agent networks, NAT traversal, encrypted communication, and multi-agent coordination with Pilot Protocol." canonicalUrl="https://pilotprotocol.network/blog/" />
</head>
<body>
  <BlogShader />
  <IslandNavbar active="blog" />
  <div class="blog-list">
    <Fragment set:html={bodyContent} />
  </div>
  <BlogFooter />
</body>
</html>
